      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1013649/" class="title-link">那个伟大的时代我们知道多少？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1013649"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/cwsea/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1059580-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cwsea/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">红了樱桃</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-12-05"
      class="main-meta">2005-12-05 11:12:53</span>
</div>

